   FPL GROUP Inc. (North Palm Beach, Fla.) -- H. Jesse
Arnelle and Stephen E. Frank were elected directors of this
utility, energy and agricultural holding company. Mr.
Arnelle, 56 years old, is a senior partner in the
California-based law firm of Arnelle &amp; Hastie. Mr. Frank, 48,
is president of FPL's Florida Power &amp; Light Co. He succeeds
Robert E. Tallon, the former president of Florida P&amp;L, who
resigned from the board in June. Mr. Arnelle is an addition
to the board and increases its size to 14 members.
