3/8 via Banca Nazionale de Lavoro.
   Japan Telecom Co. (Japan) -- 50 million Swiss francs
($35.7 million) of 7 1/2% privately placed notes due Aug. 3,
1995, priced at 100 1/4 to yield 7.44%, via Fuji Bank
(Schweiz) AG. Guaranteed by Fuji Bank in Tokyo.
