<LP>
   CINCINNATI -- Jacor Communications Inc. said it reached a
new agreement with its banks on refinancing debts, which will
allow it to defer indefinitely certain payments on
subordinated debt, warrants or capital stock.
   The action includes deferring a July 16 dividend payment
on the company's 7% cumulative preferred stock.
</LP>
